Description_lang: Casting Anti-Magic Shell grants $454863i nearby allies a Lesser Anti-Magic Shell that Absorbs up to $454863s1 magic damage and reduces the duration of harmful Magic effects against them by $454863s2%.

description_blz.en_US: Casting Anti-Magic Shell grants 2 nearby allies a Lesser Anti-Magic Shell that Absorbs up to 2,256 magic damage and reduces the duration of harmful Magic effects against them by 50%.
description_blz.es_MX: Lanzar Caparazón antimagia otorga un Caparazón antimagia menor a 2 aliados cercanos que absorbe hasta 2,256 p. de daño mágico y reduce un 50% la duración de los efectos mágicos dañinos contra ellos.
description_blz.pt_BR: Lançar Carapaça Antimagia concede a 2 aliados próximos uma Carapaça Antimagia Inferior que absorve até 2.256 de dano mágico e reduz em 50% a duração de feitos mágicos nocivos contra eles.
description_blz.de_DE: Das Wirken von 'Antimagische Hülle' gewährt 2 Verbündeten in der Nähe eine kleine antimagische Hülle, die bis zu 2.256 Magieschaden absorbiert und die Dauer aller schädlichen Magieeffekte gegen sie um 50% verringert.
description_blz.en_GB: Casting Anti-Magic Shell grants 2 nearby allies a Lesser Anti-Magic Shell that Absorbs up to 2,256 magic damage and reduces the duration of harmful Magic effects against them by 50%.
description_blz.es_ES: Al lanzar Caparazón antimagia, otorgas a 2 aliados cercanos un caparazón antimagia inferior que absorbe hasta 2256 p. de daño mágico y reduce un 50% la duración de los efectos mágicos dañinos.
description_blz.fr_FR: L’utilisation de Carapace anti-magie confère à 2 personnages alliés proches une carapace anti-magie inférieure qui absorbe jusqu’à 2256 points de dégâts magiques et réduit la durée des effets magiques néfastes contre eux de 50 %.
description_blz.it_IT: Lanciare Scudo Antimagia fornisce a 2 alleati vicini uno Scudo Antimagia Inferiore che assorbe fino a 2.256 danni magici subiti e riduce la durata degli effetti magici dannosi da loro subiti del 50%.
description_blz.ru_RU: "Антимагический панцирь" также окружает 2 находящихся рядом союзников малым антимагическим панцирем, который поглощает до 2256 ед. магического урона и сокращает время действия вредоносных магических эффектов на 50%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 대마법 보호막 시전 시 주위 아군 2명에게 하급 대마법 보호막을 부여하여 최대 2,256의 마법 피해를 흡수하고 해로운 마법 효과의 지속시간을 50%만큼 감소시킵니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 施放反魔法護罩會賦予附近2位盟友次級反魔法護罩，吸收最多2,256點魔法傷害，並使其身上的有害魔法效果的持續時間縮短50%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 施放反魔法护罩会使附近的2名盟友获得一个弱效反魔法护罩，吸收最多2,256点魔法伤害，并使其受到的有害魔法效果的持续时间缩短50%。
